<h2><a name="size" id="size">size</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntax:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;string&gt;</span>
    size_type size<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span><span class="sy0">;</span></pre>
<p>
The size method returns the number of characters in the current string.
</p>

<p>
The size method usually runs in <a href="../complexity" class="wikilink1" title="complexity">constant time</a>.
</p>

<p>
